<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Axon Setup Guide</title>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    background: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 40px 20px 80px;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 48px 52px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: #111;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 36px 0 12px;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e8e8e8;
    color: #111;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 24px 0 8px;
    color: #222;
  }

  p { margin-bottom: 12px; }

  ul, ol {
    margin: 8px 0 12px 24px;
  }

  li { margin-bottom: 4px; }

  a { color: #0070f3; text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .subtitle {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  /* Code blocks */
  .code-wrap {
    position: relative;
    margin: 14px 0 18px;
  }

  .code-lang {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    left: 14px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: #888;
    font-family: monospace;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .copy-btn {
    position: absolute;
    top: 8px;
    right: 10px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #ccc;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid #444;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .copy-btn:hover { color: #fff; border-color: #888; background: #333; }
  .copy-btn.copied { color: #4caf50; border-color: #4caf50; }

  pre {
    background: #1e1e1e;
    color: #d4d4d4;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 38px 16px 16px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    font-family: "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, monospace;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    tab-size: 2;
  }

  pre code { background: none; padding: 0; font-size: inherit; color: inherit; }

  /* Inline code */
  :not(pre) > code {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    color: #c7254e;
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  /* Syntax colours — simple keyword highlighting */
  .kw  { color: #569cd6; }   /* keywords, flags */
  .cm  { color: #6a9955; }   /* comments */
  .st  { color: #ce9178; }   /* strings */
  .fn  { color: #dcdcaa; }   /* commands / functions */
  .nm  { color: #b5cea8; }   /* numbers / ports */
  .ps  { color: #4ec9b0; }   /* PS prompt */
  .sh  { color: #9cdcfe; }   /* shell variable */

  /* Table */
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 16px 0 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  th {
    background: #f4f4f4;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
  }

  td {
    padding: 7px 12px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #fafafa; }

  hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    margin: 36px 0;
  }

  .note {
    background: #fff8e1;
    border-left: 3px solid #f9a825;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    margin: 12px 0 16px;
    color: #555;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <h1>Axon Setup Guide</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Get Axon running on a Windows PC with an NVIDIA GPU.</p>

  <h2>Requirements</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Windows PC with NVIDIA GPU (10 GB+ VRAM)</li>
    <li>Internet connection</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>

  <h2>One-Time Setup</h2>

  <h3>1. Enable WSL2</h3>
  <p>Open <strong>PowerShell as Administrator</strong> and run:</p>
  <div class="code-wrap">
    <span class="code-lang">powershell</span>
    <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
    <pre><code><span class="fn">wsl</span> <span class="kw">--install</span></code></pre>
  </div>
  <p>Restart when prompted, then install <strong>Ubuntu</strong> from the Microsoft Store.</p>

  <h3>2. Enable Virtualization in BIOS</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Go to <strong>Settings → System → Recovery → Advanced Startup → Restart Now</strong></li>
    <li>Click <strong>Troubleshoot → Advanced Options → UEFI Firmware Settings</strong></li>
    <li>Find <strong>SVM Mode</strong> (AMD) or <strong>VT-x</strong> (Intel) and set to <strong>Enabled</strong></li>
    <li>Save with <strong>F10</strong></li>
  </ol>

  <h3>3. Install NVIDIA Driver</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Go to <a href="https://www.nvidia.com/drivers" target="_blank">nvidia.com/drivers</a></li>
    <li>Download and install the <strong>Game Ready Driver</strong> for your GPU (Windows <code>.exe</code>)</li>
    <li>Install on <strong>Windows</strong> — not inside Ubuntu</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>4. Install the Project (inside Ubuntu)</h3>
  <p>Open the <strong>Ubuntu</strong> app from the Start menu and run:</p>
  <div class="code-wrap">
    <span class="code-lang">bash</span>
    <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
    <pre><code><span class="fn">sudo</span> apt update <span class="kw">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="fn">sudo</span> apt install python3 python3-pip python3-venv git <span class="kw">-y</span>
<span class="fn">git</span> clone https://github.com/oxheron/axon.git
<span class="fn">cd</span> axon
<span class="fn">git</span> checkout simplification-test
<span class="fn">python3</span> <span class="kw">-m</span> venv .venv
<span class="fn">source</span> .venv/bin/activate
<span class="fn">pip</span> install <span class="kw">-r</span> requirements.txt</code></pre>
  </div>
  <p class="note">This will take several minutes — let it finish.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>Running the System</h2>
  <p>Every time you want to run Axon, open Ubuntu and run:</p>
  <div class="code-wrap">
    <span class="code-lang">bash</span>
    <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
    <pre><code><span class="fn">cd</span> ~/axon
<span class="fn">source</span> .venv/bin/activate
<span class="sh">MODEL</span>=Qwen/Qwen2.5-3B-Instruct <span class="fn">bash</span> scripts/start.sh</code></pre>
  </div>
  <p>Wait for the <strong>"System ready!"</strong> message. This may take 3–5 minutes the first time while the model downloads and loads.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>Testing</h2>
  <p>Open a <strong>new Ubuntu tab</strong> (click the + button) and run:</p>
  <div class="code-wrap">
    <span class="code-lang">bash</span>
    <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
    <pre><code><span class="fn">cd</span> ~/axon <span class="kw">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class="fn">bash</span> scripts/test.sh</code></pre>
  </div>
  <p>You should see a response from the model. Try custom prompts:</p>
  <div class="code-wrap">
    <span class="code-lang">bash</span>
    <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
    <pre><code><span class="sh">PROMPT</span>=<span class="st">"What is the capital of France?"</span> <span class="fn">bash</span> scripts/test.sh
<span class="sh">PROMPT</span>=<span class="st">"Write a short poem about the ocean."</span> <span class="fn">bash</span> scripts/test.sh
<span class="sh">STREAM</span>=<span class="nm">1</span> <span class="fn">bash</span> scripts/test.sh   <span class="cm"># streaming mode</span></code></pre>
  </div>
  <p>Or use curl directly:</p>
  <div class="code-wrap">
    <span class="code-lang">bash</span>
    <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
    <pre><code><span class="fn">curl</span> http://localhost:<span class="nm">8080</span>/v1/chat/completions \
  <span class="kw">-H</span> <span class="st">"Content-Type: application/json"</span> \
  <span class="kw">-d</span> <span class="st">'{"model": "Qwen/Qwen2.5-3B-Instruct", "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Hello!"}], "max_tokens": 64}'</span></code></pre>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h2>Stopping the System</h2>
  <p>Press <strong>Ctrl+C</strong> in the terminal running <code>start.sh</code>. All services will shut down cleanly.</p>

  <hr>

  <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Problem</th><th>Fix</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><code>nvidia-smi</code> not found in Ubuntu</td>
        <td>Make sure you installed the NVIDIA driver on Windows and restarted</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>ray</code> command not found</td>
        <td>Run <code>source .venv/bin/activate</code> first</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Port already in use</td>
        <td>
          <div class="code-wrap" style="margin:6px 0 0">
            <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)" style="top:4px;right:6px;font-size:11px;padding:2px 7px;">Copy</button>
            <pre style="padding:10px 14px;font-size:12.5px;"><code><span class="fn">kill</span> <span class="kw">$(</span><span class="fn">lsof</span> <span class="kw">-t -i</span>:<span class="nm">8000</span> <span class="kw">-i</span>:<span class="nm">8080</span> <span class="kw">-i</span>:<span class="nm">9000</span><span class="kw">)</span> <span class="nm">2</span>>/dev/null</code></pre>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>502 Bad Gateway</td>
        <td>Wait 2–3 more minutes for the model to finish loading</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <hr>

  <h2>Architecture</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Service</th><th>Port</th><th>Role</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Coordinator</td><td><code>8000</code></td><td>Orchestrates nodes</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Node Agent</td><td><code>9000</code></td><td>Manages GPU, runs vLLM on <code>8100</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td>Inference Server</td><td><code>8080</code></td><td>User-facing API (reverse proxy)</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

</div>

<script>
  function copyCode(btn) {
    const pre = btn.closest('.code-wrap').querySelector('pre');
    const text = pre.innerText;
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(() => {
      btn.textContent = 'Copied!';
      btn.classList.add('copied');
      setTimeout(() => {
        btn.textContent = 'Copy';
        btn.classList.remove('copied');
      }, 1800);
    }).catch(() => {
      // Fallback for older browsers
      const ta = document.createElement('textarea');
      ta.value = text;
      ta.style.position = 'fixed';
      ta.style.opacity = '0';
      document.body.appendChild(ta);
      ta.select();
      document.execCommand('copy');
      document.body.removeChild(ta);
      btn.textContent = 'Copied!';
      btn.classList.add('copied');
      setTimeout(() => {
        btn.textContent = 'Copy';
        btn.classList.remove('copied');
      }, 1800);
    });
  }
</script>
</body>
</html>
